			<zhCN>冰霜女王辛达苟萨</zhCN>
		</Tag>
		<Tag enumID="184" name="CARDTEXT" type="LocString">
			<enUS>&lt;b&gt;Colossal +2&lt;/b&gt;
After an enemy minion is &lt;b&gt;Frozen&lt;/b&gt;, destroy it.</enUS>
			<zhCN>&lt;b&gt;巨型+2&lt;/b&gt;
在一个敌方随从被&lt;b&gt;冻结&lt;/b&gt;后，将其消灭。</zhCN>
		</Tag>
		<Tag enumID="351" name="FLAVORTEXT" type="LocString">
			<enUS>With her final breath, Sindragosa cursed her consort and all who abandoned her to die in Icecrown. When she was reborn by the hands of the Lich King, her first freezing exhale wrought only pain.</enUS>
			<zhCN>辛达苟萨用她最后的一丝气息，诅咒她的爱侣，以及所有任由她死在冰冠冰川的生灵。当她在巫妖王的手中重生之时，她吐出了新生的第一口寒气。那是饱含痛苦的寒气。</zhCN>
		</Tag>
